CADI.Common.LogicalTarget.JPEG2000

Class JPEG2KTile

  • java.lang.Object
    • CADI.Common.LogicalTarget.JPEG2000.JPEG2KTile
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ClientJPEG2KTile, ProxyJPEG2KTile, ServerJPEG2KTile

    public class JPEG2KTile
extends java.lang.Object
    This class stores information to deal with a tile.

    This class plays a role as a children of the CADI.Common.LogicalTarget.JPEG2000.JPEG2KCodestrea class.

    Specific parameters (COD, COC, QCD, QCC) can be set for a tile. If some of this parameters has been set, they are applied to this tile and tile-components depending of the tile. Otherwise, the default parameters defined in the JPEG2KCodestream class are applied.

    As a member of a tree structure there exist an attribute that links with the father (parent) and a table containing the children (components.

      getMethods

    • Field Detail

      • index

        protected int index
        Records the tile index.

        Only positive values are allowed.

      • parent

        protected JPEG2KCodestream parent
        Is a pointer to the parent object.

        It is useful to scan the tree structure from leaves to the root.

      • components

        protected java.util.HashMap<java.lang.Integer,JPEG2KComponent> components
        It is a hash table to store the components in which this tile is divided.

        The key of the hash is the component index.

      • codParameters

        protected CODParameters codParameters
        Coding style default (COD) for this tile.

        If this object is null the parameters to be applied to this tile are the default parameters for the codestream, JPEG2KCodestream.codParameters.

      • cocParametersList

        protected java.util.HashMap<java.lang.Integer,COCParameters> cocParametersList
        Coding style of component (COC) for this tile.

        If this object is null the parameters to be applied to this tile are the default parameters for the codestream, JPEG2KCodestream.cocParametersList.

      • qcdParameters

        protected QCDParameters qcdParameters
        Quantization default (QCD) for this tile.

        If this object is null the parameters to be applied to this tile are the default parameters for the codestream, JPEG2KCodestream.qcdParameters.

      • qccParametersList

        protected java.util.HashMap<java.lang.Integer,QCCParameters> qccParametersList
        Quantization of component (QCC) for this tile.

        If this object is null the parameters to be applied to this tile are the default parameters for the codestream, JPEG2KCodestream.qccParametersList.

      • indexes

        private CADIPoint indexes
        Indexes of the tile in terms of horizontal and vertical position.

        It is used by the getIndexes() method.

      • location

        private CADIPoint location
        Coordinates of the upper-left corner in the reference grid.

        It is used by the getLocation() method.

      • bounds

        private CADIRectangle bounds
        Bounds (location and size) of the tile in the reference grid.

        It is computed by the getBounds() method.
